{"tid":2301253,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"深灣9號複式4,460萬易手 兩年住左815萬","createTime":"2020-11-26T07:12:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T09:00:57.000Z","uid":13663,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a3359621d5b673c87011843b0651ba23bd63bd2d","tid":2301253,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T07:12:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201126/USSIGOLTKJG3NAKBZ372NI6YDA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201126%2FUSSIGOLTKJG3NAKBZ372NI6YDA%2F&d=ME9RTGLMBg%2Fi%2BHfTLk0cjNqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=f190fcb8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201126%2FUSSIGOLTKJG3NAKBZ372NI6YDA%2F&h=63663e3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201126/USSIGOLTKJG3NAKBZ372NI6YDA/</a><br />\n<br />\n第4波疫情下，豪宅市場再錄大額蝕讓。市場消息指，香港仔深灣9號3座高層C室，實用面積1,325方呎，屬於複式單位，採用4房3套房間隔，業主原本叫價4,500萬元放盤，剛以公司股權轉讓方式易手，成交價約4,460萬元，呎價33,660元。資料顯示，原業主於2018年中以購買公司股權方式入市，有指當時造價5,180萬元，至今持貨2年多轉手，疫市下賬面蝕讓720萬元，若計及代理佣金，估計實質損手約815萬元。<br />\n<br />\n圍番30幾萬住一個月都幾抵<br />\n有收租直頭有賺<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"290479a9cd5d6f97f9a04e8c25c6c29d70ea2dfc","tid":2301253,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T07:13:43.000Z","msg":"發展緊，等多幾百年先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"200b3a0ac849616450fe0eced20fa72c30438150","tid":2301253,"uid":73269,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T07:14:15.000Z","msg":"租佢單位日日賺？"},{"pid":"fd728abe8491ce701cd032e5a68d6ae8950d194e","tid":2301253,"uid":16256,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T07:14:54.000Z","msg":"又吹淡"},{"pid":"5fd6c1c15eb8b8f0ec79f6804e9bc8efbbac01d3","tid":2301253,"uid":83251,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T07:15:24.000Z","msg":"睇錯左做深圳<img s